OL,3,CBirmingham City Women investigating
OL,4,Cracist abuse at FA Cup game
OL,6,FBirmingham City Women are
OL,7,Finvestigating alleged racist abuse
OL,8,Faimed at one of their players during
OL,9,Ftheir FA Cup match against Chatham
OL,10,FTown.
OL,12,FThe targeted player, Hannah Silcock,
OL,13,Fis understood to have not heard the
OL,14,Fcomment from the supporter, but other
OL,15,Ffans have alerted the club.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
