OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1771945433
OL,3,CBirmingham City Women investigating
OL,4,Cracist abuse at FA Cup game
OL,6,FIn a post on X, Birmingham City Women
OL,7,FSupporters Group posted: "It's so
OL,8,Funfortunate that players are still
OL,9,Fbeing racially abused and something we
OL,10,Fhope is investigated by the clubs
OL,11,Finvolved.
OL,13,F"There was alleged abuse at Hannah
OL,14,FSilcock yesterday at Blues Women's FA
OL,15,FCup game of which we obviously abhor
OL,16,Fand is being looked into by Birmingham
OL,17,FCity"
OL,19,FIt is the latest report after a
OL,20,Fshocking weekend of racist abuse aimed
OL,21,Fat Premier League men's players online.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
