CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1771945433
OL,3,CBirmingham City Women investigating
OL,4,Cracist abuse at FA Cup game
OL,6,FWolves said they were 'disgusted'
OL,7,Fafter their striker Tolu Arokodare was
OL,8,Fsubjected to vile abuse after missing
OL,9,Fa penalty against Crystal Palace.
OL,11,FA few hours after the game, the club
OL,12,Freleased a statement in which they
OL,13,Fsaid they 'condemn this abhorrent and
OL,14,Funlawful behaviour in the strongest
OL,15,Fpossible terms'.
OL,17,FThey added that 'Tolu has our full and
OL,18,Funwavering support'.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
