PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1771945433
OL,3,CBirmingham City Women investigating
OL,4,Cracist abuse at FA Cup game
OL,6,FArokodare shared the private messages
OL,7,Fon his Instagram page and followed it
OL,8,Fwith a statement in which he said
OL,9,Fthose responsible should be punished.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's still unbelievable to
OL,12,Fme that we're playing in a time where
OL,13,Fpeople have so much freedom to
OL,14,Fcommunicate such racism without any
OL,15,Fconsequences.
OL,17,F"These individuals should have no
OL,18,Fplace in our game, and collectively we
OL,19,Fhave to take action to punish everyone
OL,20,Fwho taints the sport like this, no
OL,21,Fmatter who they are."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
