PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1771945433
OL,3,CBirmingham City Women investigating
OL,4,Cracist abuse at FA Cup game
OL,6,FFormer Birmingham City midfielder
OL,7,FHannibal Mejbri was another Premier
OL,8,FLeague player targeted by online
OL,9,Fabuse. Chelsea's Wesley Fofana and
OL,10,FSunderland's Romaine Mundle were also
OL,11,Fsubjected to it over the weekend.
OL,13,FBirmingham City have been contacted
OL,14,Ffor comment.
